text: Daigenis Mercedes Saturria (born 2 August 1990) is a Dominican Republic female badminton player. In 2013, she won the Carebaco International tournament in the women's doubles event partnered with Berónica Vibieca. In 2015, she also won the Carebaco International tournament in the women's and mixed doubles event and became the runner-up in the women's singles event.
